(ns o2w.api.impl
  (:require-macros [cljs.core.async.macros :refer [go go-loop]])
  (:require [ajax.core :as ajax]
            [o2w.api.cookie :as cookie]
            [reagent.core :as r]
            [cljs.core.async :refer [chan >! close! <!]]
            [o2w.i18n.db :refer [language]]))

(defn dissoc-in
  [m [k & ks :as keys]]
  (if ks
    (if-let [nextmap (get m k)]
      (let [newmap (dissoc-in nextmap ks)]
        (if (seq newmap)
          (assoc m k newmap)
          (dissoc m k)))
      m)
    (dissoc m k)))

(def TOKEN "auth_token")

;; Token
(defn get-token [] (cookie/get TOKEN))
(defn set-token [val] (cookie/set! TOKEN val))
(defn clear-token [] (cookie/set! TOKEN "") (cookie/remove! TOKEN))

(defn default-ok [res] (println res))

(defn default-error [{:keys [status] :as res}]
  (if (= status 401)
    (clear-token))
  (.log js/console res))

(defn default-headers []
  (let [token (get-token)
        csrf  (cookie/get "csrftoken")]
    (cond-> {}
      csrf      (assoc "X-CSRFToken" csrf)
      token     (assoc "Authorization" (str "Token " token))
      @language (assoc "Accept-Language" @language))))

(defonce config (r/atom {:base-url        "/api/v1/"
                         :subscriptions   {}
                         :format          (ajax.core/json-request-format)
                         :response-format (ajax.core/json-response-format {:keywords? true})
                         :interceptor     identity
                         :error           default-error
                         :headers         default-headers}))

(defn req [endpoint & [{:keys [ok error params base-url request headers interceptor]
                        :or   {ok          (:ok @config)
                               error       (:error @config)
                               base-url    (:base-url @config)
                               headers     (:headers @config)
                               interceptor (:interceptor @config)}
                        :as   args}]]

  (let [out          (chan 1)
        headers      (if (fn? headers) (headers args) headers)
        extra-params (dissoc @config :ok :error :subscriptions :base-url :headers)
        ajax-params  (merge {:uri     (str base-url endpoint)
                             :method  :get
                             :headers headers
                             :handler (fn [[ok? res]]
                                        (go
                                          (>! out [ok? res])
                                          (close! out))

                                        (if ok?
                                          (when ok (ok res))
                                          (error res)))}
                            extra-params
                            args
                            {:params (interceptor params)})

        ajax-request (ajax.core/ajax-request ajax-params)]

    (when request
      (when @request (ajax/abort @request))
      (reset! request ajax-request))

    out))
